#  _migratum ‚Äî cl-migratum: Database schema migration system for Common Lisp
#
#  Source-direct extraction from
#    https://github.com/dnaeon/cl-migratum/blob/master/src/cli/main.lisp
#    https://github.com/dnaeon/cl-migratum/blob/master/src/cli/migrate.lisp
